{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 58,
  "title": "第五十八章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "其政悶悶，其民淳淳；"
    },
    {
      "text": "其政察察，其民缺缺。"
    },
    {
      "text": "禍兮福之所倚，福兮禍之所伏。孰知其極？其無正。"
    },
    {
      "text": "正復為奇，"
    },
    {
      "text": "善復為妖。"
    },
    {
      "text": "人之迷，其日固久。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人方而不割，"
    },
    {
      "text": "廉而不劌，"
    },
    {
      "text": "直而不肆，"
    },
    {
      "text": "光而不燿。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言善治政者，無形無名，無事無政可舉，悶悶然，卒至於大治，故曰，其政悶悶也。其民無所爭競，寬大淳淳，故曰，其民淳淳也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "立刑名，明賞罰，以檢姦偽，故曰察察也。殊類分析，民懷爭競，故曰，其民缺缺也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 23
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言誰知善治之極乎！唯無可正舉，無可形名，悶悶然而天下大化，是其極也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以正治國，則便復以奇用兵矣。故曰，正復為奇。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "立善以和萬物，則便復有妖之患也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人之迷惑失道，固久矣。不可便正善治以責。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以方導物，舍去其邪，不以方割物，所謂大方無隅。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "廉，清廉也；劌，傷也。以清廉清民，令去其邪，令去其汙，不以清廉劌傷於物也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以直導物，令去其僻，而不以直激沸於物也。所謂大直若屈也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以光鑑其所以迷，不以光照求其隱慝也，所謂明道若昧也，此皆崇本以息末，不攻而使復之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
